	<!-- COPPER -->
		<ThingDef ParentName="TMM_IngotBase">
			<defName>TMM_Ingot_Copper</defName>
			<label>copper</label>
			<description>An orange-looking, relatively malleable and somewhat pretty metal that can be found in veins scattered in mountains. Copper is not very tough, but somewhat viable for weaponry in some rare cases, however, it has very high thermal and electrical conductivity, and it is mostly used as a temperature insulator and electrical conductor. Copper is essential in modern civilizations and settlements as the main element used to make wiring and generators. Its use is also widely required in electronics. Copper is a naturally sterile metal and has a very slight bonus to cleanliness.</description>

			<graphicData>
				<color>(236,146,121)</color>
			</graphicData>

			<statBases>
				<MarketValue>0.9</MarketValue>
				<Mass>0.3</Mass>
				<StuffPower_Armor_Sharp>0.8</StuffPower_Armor_Sharp>
				<StuffPower_Armor_Blunt>0.38</StuffPower_Armor_Blunt>
